  "detailed_description": "Easy to play, very hard to finish. Can you beat <strong>The World's Hardest Game 3D Nostalgia 2</strong>?<br><br><strong>The World's Hardest Game 2</strong>, which you used to play on flash game sites, is now with you in 3D. <strong>The same 50 levels in the original game</strong>, waiting for you in 3D!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590160/extras/dbe67c9fd053f4f66a2391e39a7eb9a3.webp?t=1695419387\" width=235 height=54 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>50 different levels!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Carefully crafted detailed levels, same as in the original game</strong><br></li><li><strong>Smooth gameplay</strong><br></li><li><strong>Cute graphics and colorful atmosphere</strong><br></li><li><strong>Long playing time and challenging levels</strong><br></li><li><strong>Auto save system</strong><br></li><li><strong>NOSTALGIA !!</strong></li></ul><br><strong>Collect diamonds to unlock next level and unique achievements!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590160/extras/13e2d8cbd005ae5e3c2ff9fdc7f0bbf9.poster.avif?t=1695419387\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590160/extras/13e2d8cbd005ae5e3c2ff9fdc7f0bbf9.webm?t=1695419387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590160/extras/13e2d8cbd005ae5e3c2ff9fdc7f0bbf9.mp4?t=1695419387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can use a <strong>bird's eye view</strong> to analyze the level you are in. But remember, you cannot move while in <strong>bird's eye view</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590160/extras/5fc0271c5919236ef2af9e2ba6f755c1.poster.avif?t=1695419387\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590160/extras/5fc0271c5919236ef2af9e2ba6f755c1.webm?t=1695419387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590160/extras/5fc0271c5919236ef2af9e2ba6f755c1.mp4?t=1695419387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
